            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1684236079357-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>salmon fillet[s]</strong> to a plate with your<strong> tamari soy sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>tamari-marinated salmon</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
