    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>with your<strong> mayo</strong> and a squeeze of <strong>lime </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p>",
