            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Layer the <strong>crispy rice patties</strong> with the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>sliced avocado </strong>and<strong> tamari salmon </strong>on top</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong>, your<strong> black sesame seeds </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
